title: There Is A Dog In The Studio + Big Sean & Kanye In The Studio + Parrot Heads

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/19/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are back in the studio - Ebro pays goes off about public spending (33), and still doesn't love Way 2 Sexy (25). The crew discusses Rosenberg's dog which is in the studio and enjoy some White Ish.
